<div class="container">
	<div class="hero-unit">
        <h1>New Landlord</h1>
        <hr style="border: 1px solid black;"/>
        <p>We must not have any listings from your landlord yet! Fill out the fields below to add your landlord to our database. Thanks!</p>
        <br />
        <%= form_for(@landlord) do |f| %>
  			<%= render 'shared/error_messages', :object => f.object %>

    		<%= f.text_field :name, :placeholder => "Landlord Name" %>
    		<br />
  			<%= f.text_field :address, :placeholder => "Address" %>
  			<br />
    		<%= f.text_field :email, :placeholder => "Email" %>
    		<br />
    		<%= f.text_field :website, :placeholder => "Website" %>
    		<br />
    		<%= f.text_field :phone, :placeholder => "Phone number" %>
    		<br />
  			<%= f.text_field :city, :placeholder => "City" %>
  			<br />
    		<%= f.text_field :state, :placeholder => "Wisconsin", :disabled => :true %>
    		<br />
  			<%= f.text_field :zip, :placeholder => "Zip Code" %>	
  			<br /><br />
    		<%= f.submit "Add Landlord", :class => "btn-large btn-inverse" %>
		<% end %>
	
		<p>Ideally, here we have a group of check box that allows them to choose
  		listings that are associated with this landlord...but I'm not sure 
  		how that would work/don't have the time yet,
  		so it may have to wait for another day.</p>
  		
	</div><!--./hero-unit -->
